search_results.title: Carl Seaton
search_results.snippet: Carl Seaton is an award-nominated director and filmmaker, known for his work in episodic television. Born in Chicago, Carl's story begins as a little kid.

search_results.title: Carl Seaton
search_results.snippet: Carl Seaton was born on 10 November 1971 in Chicago, Illinois, USA. He is a director and writer, known for One Week (2000), Snowfall (2017) and Interface.
